Game

Game
  - title
  - has_many assets
  - has_many trials

  Game::NBack:


  Trial
    - game_id
    - has_many turns
    - maxTurns
    - has_one user, null: true
    - completed?

    GameTurn
      - belongs_to user
      - belongs_to Trial
      - has_one user_selection
      - has_one cpu_selection
      - **game-specific processes**
        nback processes:
          - display cell
          - play sound

    Choice
      - belongs_to Turn
      - type: string (user/cpu)
      - initialize with cpu_selection
      - user_selection: reference



  Asset
    - game_id

    AudioFile < Asset
      - path

    Note < Asset
      - name
      - noteNum
      - interval(note)

    Cell < Asset
      Cell (n-back) < Cell
        - position
        - audio

      Cell (esp) < Cell
        - position
        - picture
